title: What NFT should we add to the Nom Noms DAO?
body:
Vote on which NFT you would like to see added to the Nom Noms DAO! Our budget for this voting is 4.94553988 ETH

DAO wallet can be viewed in Gnosis Safe App.

https://gnosis-safe.io/app/#/safes/0xF193B0895e0F5BbA8B0a6a1f1194fd1260536f7D/balances

We will also be utilizing https://fractional.art/ to allow us to buy fractional shares of high-value blue-chip NFTs such as CryptoPunks, Cool Cats, and such.
author: 0x183E1f773A204dC836D836147A44735c50F006F4
